	<h4> Vacancies</h4> <br><br>
	<p><strong>Pending Requisitions:</strong> 
Details about the requisitions which have been posted by the HOD(s) but have not yet been approved by the management. 
The requesting HOD can resend the same form for approval to the management heads.<br><br>
	
	<strong>Approved Vacancies:</strong> 
 HR : receive a mail notification for each approved requisition, Clicking on the Proceed option he will be able to promote the job on social networking sites and send an email to all the employees notifying them about the vacancy opened and link to Employee Referral form.
HOD: Receive an email notification for the approved requisition.<br><br>
	
	<strong>Opened Vacancies:</strong>
Clicking on the View Details option, it will show details of that particular round, which candidates qualified it and where they are currently with their status and CES. 
Link to Employee Referral Form.
Additional access to HR: Screen Candidates for each job, schedule number of rounds, name of each round. Schedule/Reschedule interviews  for each candidate in every round. After final selection of candidate, get approval by the management, check reference for the candidate, after final joining of candidate, close the vacancy.<br><br>

	<strong>Closed Vacancies:</strong>
Details about the filled positions. View Details will show the list of selected candidates, date of closing.<br><br><div class="well"><img src="img/vacncies.png" /></div><br><br>

<h4> Scheduler</h4> <br><br>
<strong>For HR</strong><br><br>
<ul><li>The HR has the access to schedule interviews for each round of every requisition. Clicking on the Scheduler option for any round of an interview the HR will be directed to the Scheduler Page.</li><br>
<li>Scheduler will contain a brief detail about the requisition( job designation, requisition bye, Date of request and date of approval).</li><br>
<li>Shortlisted candidate list, HR will assign the location, interview date, time and panel of interviewers for each candidate.</li><br>
<li>If interviewers have already been assigned for a specific date and time, while scheduling interview for the next candidate at the same date and time their names will be removed from the Interviewer pool.</li></ul>
<br><br><div class="well"><img src="img/Scheduler.png" /></div>
<br><br>
<strong>For Interviewer</strong><br><br>
<ul><li>Interviewer views the candidates to be interviewed.</li><br><br>
<li>In case of inability in being present at the scheduled time, he enters the reason for inability to take the interview, clicks on the Send to HR button which will send a notifying email to the HR and he will reschedule the process.</li><br><br>
<li>Clicking on Candidates' Name, candidate details are shown along with their CV and link to the Candidate Evaluation Sheet to be filled after the interview of each candidate. Candidate Evaluation Report of previous rounds(if any).</li></ul><br><br>
